{
  "texts": [
    "His research has been focused on the application of multi-sensor satellite measurements to monitor changes in the Earth's hydrosphere and atmosphere.",
    "He is an expert in developing signal processing techniques based on statistical decomposition, Bayesian inversion, and data assimilation techniques.X.",
    "He is an Associate Professor at the School of Civil and Surveying & Mapping Engineering, Jiangxi University of Science and Technology (China).",
    "His research interest includes GNSS high-precision positioning, sea-level change, and surface mass loading modeling.",
    "He is also involved in the application of neural networks to extract information from various datasets."
  ]
}